<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 12:14:53 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列部长赞扬法国极右党主席，打破以色列官方抵制全国集会的行为</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/minister-praises-frances-far-right-party-president-breaking-israels-official-boycott/00000190-53c3-d31c-afb9-dfd39a180000</link><description>侨民部长阿米凯·奇克利（Amichai Chikli）赞扬了法国极右翼全国集会主席乔丹·巴尔德拉（Jordan Bardella）发表的讲话，他在讲话中宣布两国解决方案“过时”，巴勒斯坦建国是“恐怖的奖励”。奇克利办公室：“我们与勒庞党有良好的接触”</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 11:43:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/minister-praises-frances-far-right-party-president-breaking-israels-official-boycott/00000190-53c3-d31c-afb9-dfd39a180000</guid></item><item><title>“犹太人，滚出这座城市！”：犹太儿童在伦敦涉嫌仇恨犯罪中遭到袭击</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/get-out-of-the-city-jew-jewish-children-assaulted-in-alleged-hate-crime-in-london/00000190-5401-de5e-abd0-ff73cf470000</link><description>一群东正教男孩在中央地铁站遭到当地另一所学校的孩子们的袭击。其中一名男孩的母亲说：“他们把他的头撞到墙上，一颗牙齿脱落了。”</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 10:43:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/get-out-of-the-city-jew-jewish-children-assaulted-in-alleged-hate-crime-in-london/00000190-5401-de5e-abd0-ff73cf470000</guid></item><item><title>“黎巴嫩的战争不会是与真主党的决斗；以色列将面临伊朗的整个抵抗轴心”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-26/ty-article-podcast/in-a-war-with-hezbollah-israel-will-face-irans-entire-axis-of-resistance/00000190-53a1-de5e-abd0-fbf3be140000</link><description></description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 10:06:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/podcasts/2024-06-26/ty-article-podcast/in-a-war-with-hezbollah-israel-will-face-irans-entire-axis-of-resistance/00000190-53a1-de5e-abd0-fbf3be140000</guid></item><item><title>正统派并不急于退出政府，但最高法院对草案问题的裁决扩大了联盟的裂痕</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/haredim-in-no-hurry-to-exit-govt-but-top-court-ruling-widens-cracks-in-the-coalition/00000190-53c0-ddd9-a1f1-d3f286b30000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡对裁决的回应具有误导性和煽动性。一些人预计他会继续宣传甘茨的“豁免法”，只是为了争取时间，因为他知道法院会否决它</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 10:00:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/haredim-in-no-hurry-to-exit-govt-but-top-court-ruling-widens-cracks-in-the-coalition/00000190-53c0-ddd9-a1f1-d3f286b30000</guid></item><item><title>两名士兵在加沙非装甲坦克爆炸中丧生后，以色列军队收紧了协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/idf-tightens-protocols-after-two-soldiers-die-in-explosion-of-non-armored-tank-in-gaza/00000190-536e-de5e-abd0-fb7e0c780000</link><description>&amp;#39;那是一个错误。消息人士称，这付出了沉重的代价，因为在调查士兵死亡事件时，以色列陆军指令下令在南部前线的每辆坦克上安装铭牌</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 09:04:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/idf-tightens-protocols-after-two-soldiers-die-in-explosion-of-non-armored-tank-in-gaza/00000190-536e-de5e-abd0-fb7e0c780000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯官员相信，只有在以色列国防军离开拉法之后，美国才会向以色列施压以达成协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/hamas-officials-believe-u-s-will-pressure-israel-for-a-deal-only-after-idf-leaves-rafah/00000190-5361-de5e-abd0-fb7383390000</link><description>一名巴勒斯坦官员表示，哈马斯领导人确信美国不会努力达成停火，而是会拖延直到加沙的激烈战斗结束。他说，以色列军队离开拉法可能是“在各方，特别是美国人放弃之前重新启动谈判的最后机会”</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 08:42:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/hamas-officials-believe-u-s-will-pressure-israel-for-a-deal-only-after-idf-leaves-rafah/00000190-5361-de5e-abd0-fb7383390000</guid></item><item><title>以色列最高法院即使没有组建新政府，也可能为新的正统派犹太人铺平道路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-may-have-paved-the-way-for-the-new-haredi-jew-if-not-a-new-government/00000190-5141-de50-af9b-7fed1c6c0000</link><description>高等法院强制征召犹太学生的裁决不会让内塔尼亚胡的联盟垮台，因为他和他的极端正统派伙伴只是想避免不可避免的事情</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 03:02:55 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-top-court-may-have-paved-the-way-for-the-new-haredi-jew-if-not-a-new-government/00000190-5141-de50-af9b-7fed1c6c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列负担沉重的公众感到沮丧。它不会让军方通过象征性的正统征兵而逃脱惩罚</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-frustrated-public-wont-let-the-military-get-away-with-a-symbolic-haredi-draft/00000190-50e3-de50-af9b-7fef8e770000</link><description>加沙正在进行的战争凸显了以色列国防军服役人员与国家豁免人员之间的不平等有多么严重。法院的裁决为新的服役模式和替代的国民服役形式创造了机会。如果参谋长联手回避这个问题，一波愤怒可能会危及“人民军队”模式</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 03:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article/.premium/israels-frustrated-public-wont-let-the-military-get-away-with-a-symbolic-haredi-draft/00000190-50e3-de50-af9b-7fef8e770000</guid></item><item><title>美国：与真主党的战争将是“灾难性的”； Gallant：以色列更倾向于外交解决方案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article-live/u-s-war-with-hezbollah-would-be-catastrophic-gallant-israel-prefers-diplomacy/00000190-524c-d37f-a392-7aee8aa30000</link><description>数百人在以色列各地示威，作为全国抗议日的一部分 ■ 以色列国防军击毙了向加沙地带走私武器的哈马斯特工 ■ 《华尔街日报》：官员称，由于以色列提出的新要求减少，美国武器运输速度放缓 ■ 以色列国防军向一架坠落的无人机发射了拦截器在埃拉特附近的红海，没有进入以色列领土</description><pubDate>Wed, 26 Jun 2024 02:17:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-26/ty-article-live/u-s-war-with-hezbollah-would-be-catastrophic-gallant-israel-prefers-diplomacy/00000190-524c-d37f-a392-7aee8aa30000</guid></item><item><title>联盟高级消息人士担心，如果以色列军队征兵法未能在七月最后期限前通过，政府就不会垮台</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/senior-coalition-sources-fear-collapse-if-conscription-law-doesnt-pass-by-july-deadline/00000190-5069-de50-af9b-7fed94820000</link><description>虽然内塔尼亚胡政府相信联盟将能够经受住周二高等法院反对极端正统军队豁免的裁决的风暴，但他们担心，如果他们提议的征兵法没有在议会获得通过，联盟可能会分崩离析</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 18:39:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/senior-coalition-sources-fear-collapse-if-conscription-law-doesnt-pass-by-july-deadline/00000190-5069-de50-af9b-7fed94820000</guid></item><item><title>最高法院对正统派法律草案的裁决令极端正统派政党陷入混乱，并使内塔尼亚胡的联盟面临风险</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/top-court-ruling-send-ultra-orthodox-parties-scrambling-puts-netanyahu-coalition-at-risk/00000190-507a-d3c0-a5d4-737a0c910000</link><description>以色列最高法院决定命令国家征召正统派人士，并停止向不合作的犹太教派提供资金，这让极端正统派政党陷入了严重的困境。虽然他们不排除解散议会的可能性，但他们明白他们没有真正的政治选择</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 18:15:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/top-court-ruling-send-ultra-orthodox-parties-scrambling-puts-netanyahu-coalition-at-risk/00000190-507a-d3c0-a5d4-737a0c910000</guid></item><item><title>以色列总检察长命令国防机构立即招募 3,000 名极端正统派加入以色列国防军</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-orders-defense-establishment-to-immediately-recruit-3-000-ultra-orthodox/00000190-5026-d3c0-a5d4-7366941a0000</link><description>以色列高等法院一致裁定极端正统派男子有义务服兵役几个小时后，总检察长加利·巴哈拉夫-米亚拉致信国防部长和政府，表示国家必须遵守法院的裁决，并立即开始军队服役。流程草案</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 17:07:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/israels-ag-orders-defense-establishment-to-immediately-recruit-3-000-ultra-orthodox/00000190-5026-d3c0-a5d4-7366941a0000</guid></item><item><title>10月7日，特朗普认可了一部有关哈马斯强奸的电影。他只是忘记提及强奸事件</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-25/ty-article/.highlight/trump-endorsed-a-film-about-hamas-rape-on-october-7-he-just-forgot-to-mention-the-rape/00000190-5018-d91c-abba-ff1844930000</link><description>特朗普在出人意料地呼吁观看有关哈马斯性暴力的纪录片《沉默前的尖叫》时表示，该纪录片“生动地描绘了哈马斯所造成的死亡和破坏。”这把他的主张变成了一种否认</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 16:52:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-25/ty-article/.highlight/trump-endorsed-a-film-about-hamas-rape-on-october-7-he-just-forgot-to-mention-the-rape/00000190-5018-d91c-abba-ff1844930000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 263 天：联合国停止在加沙的援助行动，直到工人得到更好的保护</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-263-un-to-halt-aid-ops-in-gaza-until-workers-are-better-protected/00000190-5019-d8cb-a19d-595b23550000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡高级助手表示不可能让哈马斯消失 ■ 哈马斯政治局主席伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚的妹妹在以色列对加沙城的袭击中丧生 ■ 据报道，巴勒斯坦总统阿巴斯将访问俄罗斯 ■ 总理内塔尼亚胡的妻子告诉人质的家人，她认为以色列国防军领导人想要上演反对她丈夫的政变 ■ 战争进入 263 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 16:23:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-263-un-to-halt-aid-ops-in-gaza-until-workers-are-better-protected/00000190-5019-d8cb-a19d-595b23550000</guid></item><item><title>巴勒斯坦权力机构内部的权力斗争正好影响了以色列削弱巴勒斯坦权力机构的计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/power-struggles-within-palestinian-authority-play-into-israels-plans-of-weakening-it/00000190-4dfb-d8cb-a19d-4dfb722f0000</link><description>巴勒斯坦振兴巴解组织的倡议遭到巴勒斯坦权力机构的严厉批评。这些内部斗争影响了以色列控制加沙地带、加强对约旦河西岸的控制以及导致巴勒斯坦唯一代表机构崩溃的计划。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:14:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/power-struggles-within-palestinian-authority-play-into-israels-plans-of-weakening-it/00000190-4dfb-d8cb-a19d-4dfb722f0000</guid></item><item><title>“时间不多了”：加兰特敦促美国与以色列合作应对伊朗威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/gallant-to-blinken-eyes-of-enemies-on-u-s-israel-ties-dispute-must-be-solved-quickly/00000190-4fb2-d91c-abba-efb228cc0000</link><description>在访问华盛顿期间，以色列国防部长告诉美国国防部长帮助以色列应对伊朗核计划迫在眉睫的威胁。加兰特还告诉布林肯，“我们敌人的眼睛”关注着以色列与美国的紧张局势，并表示他们的争端必须迅速解决</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 15:08:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/gallant-to-blinken-eyes-of-enemies-on-u-s-israel-ties-dispute-must-be-solved-quickly/00000190-4fb2-d91c-abba-efb228cc0000</guid></item><item><title>守门员和维和人员：以色列基布兹尼克、贝都因人和撤离人员团结起来踢足球</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/goal-and-peace-keepers-israeli-kibbutzniks-bedouin-and-evacuees-unite-for-soccer-tourney/00000190-4ec8-d91c-abba-efd8a5d80000</link><description>为了保持传统和理智，米什马尔哈埃梅克基布兹 (Kibbutz Mishmar HaEmek) 的居民、卡阿比耶村 (Ka&amp;#39;abiyye) 和纳哈尔奥兹 (Nahal Oz) 的撤离人员联合起来参加足球比赛。每个人都是赢家</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 14:38:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/sports/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/goal-and-peace-keepers-israeli-kibbutzniks-bedouin-and-evacuees-unite-for-soccer-tourney/00000190-4ec8-d91c-abba-efd8a5d80000</guid></item><item><title>黎巴嫩政界人士、专家和民众担心以色列和真主党之间爆发全面战争</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/fearing-israel-hezbollah-all-out-war-lebanese-politicians-pundits-and-people-speak-out/00000190-4f4a-d8cb-a19d-4f4b8e660000</link><description>随着#LebanonDoesNotWantAWar 标签在社交媒体上流行，黎巴嫩主要政客寻求缓和局势，神职人员谴责“犹太复国主义干涉”，黎巴嫩公民公开批评真主党</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 14:19:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/fearing-israel-hezbollah-all-out-war-lebanese-politicians-pundits-and-people-speak-out/00000190-4f4a-d8cb-a19d-4f4b8e660000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡的高级顾问表示“哈马斯是一个想法”，无法用武力击败，加沙需要替代方案</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/pms-top-adviser-hamas-is-an-idea-that-cant-be-beaten-by-force-gaza-needs-alternative/00000190-4f8c-d3c0-a5d4-6fee02190000</link><description>以色列国家安全负责人查奇·哈内比周一在安全会议上表示，以色列需要提出替代哈马斯在加沙统治的方案，“而不仅仅是摧毁其军事能力”。上周，以色列国防军发言人也说了同样的话，很快遭到总理批评</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 14:19:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/pms-top-adviser-hamas-is-an-idea-that-cant-be-beaten-by-force-gaza-needs-alternative/00000190-4f8c-d3c0-a5d4-6fee02190000</guid></item><item><title>总理的妻子萨拉·内塔尼亚胡告诉人质家属，军队首长希望发动政变反对她的丈夫</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-wife-tells-hostage-families-idf-chiefs-want-to-stage-coup-against-her-husband/00000190-4f8c-d8cb-a19d-4fcf448c0000</link><description>在与少数人质家庭的一次小型会议上，总理的妻子一再表示她不信任军队领导人。代表内塔尼亚胡夫人的发言人表示，有关内塔尼亚胡夫人的虚假、有倾向性和持续的泄密行为构成了令人发指的不公正行为。</description><pubDate>Tue, 25 Jun 2024 13:55:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-25/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-wife-tells-hostage-families-idf-chiefs-want-to-stage-coup-against-her-husband/00000190-4f8c-d8cb-a19d-4fcf448c0000</guid></item></channel></rss>